cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with pose detection and face detection, which are core topics in computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a generative model (pix2pix) and k-NN for pose transfer, which are machine learning techniques. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with generating videos of people performing actions, which can be seen as an AI task. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating videos, which can be seen as a graphics task. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with video processing and generation, which are core topics in multimedia.
